{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"01c4fbe4a2","title":"致刘伯承、邓小平等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2161b2de43","index":0,"year":1947,"month":7,"day":27,"articleId":"01c4fbe4a2"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji23","name":"毛泽东全集第23卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji23.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji23":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fe905573f6","type":"paragraph","text":"致刘伯承、邓小平等电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"01c4fbe4a2"},{"id":"ec7ccbfdc0","type":"paragraph","text":"1947年7月27日）速令到达像皖苏边区的张才干、李人林两部加紧整训，务子八月二十五日以前整训完毕，届时随刘、邓南下，恢复鄂豫皖工作[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的致刘伯承、邓小平、郑位三、李[2]指以张才千为司令员兼政治委员、李人格为副司令员兼副政治委员的中原游击织队所辅第一、第四支队。该两部于1947年6月到达豫皖苏解放区，整训后编为中原独立旅。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"01c4fbe4a2"}],"page":{"id":"3d6e85d8f5","publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"01c4fbe4a2","start":166,"end":166}}}},"__N_SSG":true}